sources.title: Blackout | Part 1 of 2 | FULL MOVIE | Action, Espionage | James Brolin, Anne Heche, Haylie Duff
sources.description:
Part 1: A computer hacker, recruited by a shadowy figure, has executed the largest disaster to hit California—shutting down the state’s vulnerable electrical system. Agent Strickland of Homeland Security’s Cyber Terrorism Division enlists a squadron of experts to outwit the source of the blackout.

Watch part 2 here!: https://youtu.be/G86HHHVzk60
